[I agree with Adrian Gibbs' comment. In my own comments on the story that
was posted, I indicated that this report needed to be confirmed. Whether
others will attempt to confirm the story remains to be seen; from the
description of the research in Polar Biology, it looks like it would be a
herculean task. - Mod.DH]
